    "AI applications can analyze students' schedules, workload, and learning habits to provide personalized recommendations for effective study plans and time management.",
    "This can help students balance their academic responsibilities and avoid burnout.",
    "The use of AI for managing student learning was reported by Crompton and Burke [1].",
    "Among others, the researchers reported on identification of learning patterns, curriculum sequencing, instructional design, student management, and provision of information and organization.",
    "Language translation and supportStudents can practice language skills via, for example, AI-powered chatbots that can answer their questions [4]."
